    </nav>
    <header>
        <h2>web development that's out of this world</h2>
        <a href="#contact" class="button" role="button">Contact Us</a>
        <div id="quote">
            <div class="separator"></div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section id="smallTagline">
        <p>Astra is a web development company that designs & builds websites for small businesses - with benefits that
            you won't
            find in other webdev businesses.</p>
    </section>
    <Section heading="whyUs" subheading="">
        <div class="rowContainer">
            <Row heading="WordPress websites are slow. Our websites are blazing-fast">
                <div class="row-inner">
                    <p>Many of our competitors use tools like WordPress, which allow them to create a website quickly
                        and
                        easily, but end up creating a slower site</p>
                    <p>WordPress is a dynamic site generator, which means every time someone visits your website, it has
                        to
                        do a bunch of processing to serve the name, content, etc. With us, we directly code it into your
                        website,
                        so it loads lightning-fast!</p>
                    <p>In effect, slower sites are heavily penalized, so they appear lower in Google Search and Maps. 3%
                        of customers
                        leave a website every second it takes to load.</p>
                </div>
            </Row>
            <Row heading="Our websites don't require any maintenance.">
                <div class="row-inner">
                    <p>With other website creators, you have to worry about your WordPress and plugins not getting
                        hacked.
                    </p>
                    <p>With us, you don't need to update plugins or make sure the website
                        is working.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </Row>
            <Row heading="Mobile-centered by design.">
                <div class="row-inner">
                    <p>Every website nowadays needs to look well on phones, and we focus our development on building
                        good-looking websites.</p>
                </div>
        </Row>
		</div>
        <h4 class="tagline">We make custom static websites that perform<em> better </em>than our competitors and can
            help increase your customers.</h4>
		</Section>
    <Section heading="Wanna look at our portfolio?" subheading="">
        <app-portfolio-container>
            <app-portfolio-tab name="Webdev">
                <image-carousel></image-carousel>

            </app-portfolio-tab>
