        <ul>
            <li><a href="demo-websites/product-design-1">IO RetroPlayer PRO (demo)</a></li>
            <li><a href="demo-websites/farm-1">Farm (demo)</a></li>
            <li><a href="demo-websites/gaming-1">Gaming (demo)</a></li>
        </ul>
        <image-carousel></image-carousel>
    </Section>
    <Section heading="All in means all in." subheading="">
        <span>No additional hosting costs.</span>
        <span>No buying domains.</span>
        <span>Just give us a bit of information, and we'll get to work.</span>
        <span>And in the future, we may be able to handle marketing and other important operations, too!</span>

	</Section>
