    <Section heading="Pricing" subheading="Simple Pricing">
        <div class="card">
            <h5>Monthly</h5>
            <span>All-in. Everything you need for your business's online presence.</span>
            <span class="priceOuter"><span class="priceInner">$80</span>/month</span>
            <ul>
                <li>Basic Google Business Profile setup</li>
                <li>Included hosting & domain</li>
                <li>Unlimited Updates</li>
                <li>Analytics setup via Google or Plausible</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="bold">Note: You must pay for at least 9 months.</span>
        </div>
    </Section>
    <section id="about">
        <h3>about</h3>
        <Row heading="">
            <div>
                <h4>hi. i'm jose sanchez.</h4>
                <p>I'm a designer and developer of websites and software products. I've had a significant amount of
                    experience in webdev, having an internship making webapps since my senior year of high school, and
                    participating in other internships and computer science-related programs since. I'm
                    currently studying CS in college, so know that your business will help a student out!
                    :)</p>
                <a class="button" role="button" href="https://josesanchez.dev">View Personal Portfolio/website</a>
                <!-- UPDATE WHEN PORTFOLIO WEBSITE GOES LIVE -->
            </div>
            <img src="#" />
        </Row>
    </section>
    <section id="contact">
        <h3>ready for web development that's awesome?</h3>
        <p>Enter your details, and I'll give you a call whenever I have time.</p>
        <form name="newProject">
            <input type="text" required name="name" placeholder="Your name" />
            <input type="email" required name="email" placeholder="Your email" />
            <input type="tel" required name="phoneNumber" placeholder="Your phone number" />
            <input type="text" required name="projectTitle" placeholder="Your project title" />
            <span>We need a description for your project. Make sure to include references (designs, if you have any, or
                similar websites).</span>
            <textarea name="projectDescription" placeholder="Please add a description of your project." cols="7"></textarea>
            <span>What times would you be available to talk about your project?</span>
            <div><label for="early">Early</label>
                <input type="checkbox" name="early" />
            </div>
            <div><label for="noon">Noon</label>
                <input type="checkbox" name="noon" />
            </div>
            <div><label for="afternoon">Afternoon</label>
                <input type="checkbox" name="afternoon" />
            </div>
            <span>And what days?</span>
            <div id="days">
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Monday" />
                    <label for="Monday">Monday</label>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Tuesday" />
                    <label for="Tuesday">Tuesday</label>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Wednesday" />
                    <label for="Wednesday">Wednesday</label>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Thursday" />
                    <label for="Thursday">Thursday</label>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Friday" />
                    <label for="Friday">Friday</label>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Saturday" />
                    <label for="Saturday">Saturday</label>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="Sunday" />
                    <label for="Sunday">Sunday</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <input type="submit" value="Send" />

        </form>
        <div id="sphere">
        </div>
    </section>
